  <questiontext format="html"><text><![CDATA[<p>Let \(N\sim\mathrm{Poisson}(\lambda)\) and \(X_i\) i.i.d. with \(E[X_i]=0\) and \(\mathrm{Var}(X_i)=\sigma^2\), independent of \(N\). Then \(\mathrm{Var}(X_1+\cdots+X_N)\) is:</p>]]></text></questiontext>
